  <!-- About Section -->
  <div id="about" class="card mb-4 w-100" style="min-height: 300px; margin-top: 80px;">
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center text-center">
          <h2 class="card-title mb-3">About Our PG Accommodation Finder</h2>
          <p class="card-text">
              Welcome to our PG Finder platform! We aim to make finding and booking Paying Guest accommodations seamless and convenient. 
              Whether you're a student, working professional, or someone seeking a comfortable stay, our platform connects you with a variety of PG options 
              tailored to meet your unique needs. Our mission is to help you find a home away from home with ease.
          </p>
          <p class="card-text">
              Explore a wide range of accommodations, each equipped with amenities like Wi-Fi, meals, laundry services, and more. 
              Enjoy a hassle-free experience as you compare options and make the best choice with just a few clicks.
          </p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary mb-2" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#requirementModal">
              <i class="bi bi-chat-fill mx-2"></i>Share Requirement
          </button>
      </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How to Use Section -->
  <div class="card mb-4 w-100" style="min-height: 300px;">
