          <p class="card-text">
              To unlock all features, please <a href="/auth/page/login/student">login</a> or <a href="/auth/page/register/student">register</a>.
              Once you're logged in, you can explore a variety of PG accommodations, apply filters to find the best match based on 
              location, price, and amenities, and book your preferred option in minutes. 
          </p>
          <p class="card-text">
              Our user-friendly interface guides you through every step, from browsing listings to completing your booking. 
              Start your search today and discover your ideal accommodation with ease!
          </p>
      </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <div id="contact" class="container my-5">
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-5 mb-4">
              <h3>About Us</h3>
              <p>Welcome to our PG Finder platform! We're here to help you find comfortable, convenient accommodations that meet your needs. Reach out to us through our social media or email, and we'll be happy to assist.</p>
              <h5>Contact Information</h5>
              <p><strong>Email:</strong> contact@pgfinder.com</p>
              <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 234 567 890</p>
              <h5>Follow Us</h5>
              <p>
                  <a href="https://facebook.com" class="text-decoration-none me-3"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i> Facebook</a>
                  <a href="https://twitter.com" class="text-decoration-none me-3"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i> Twitter</a>
                  <a href="https://instagram.com" class="text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i> Instagram</a>
              </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-7">
              <h3>Contact Us</h3>
              <form id="contactForm" action="/submit-contact" method="POST">
                  <div class="mb-3">
                      <label for="name" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your name.</div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="mb-3">
                      <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
                      <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter a valid email address.</div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="mb-3">
                      <label for="subject" class="form-label">Subject</label>
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="subject" name="subject" required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter the subject of your message.</div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="mb-3">
                      <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
                      <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your message.</div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
              </form>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>

